title: Raley's
description: A conventional grocery store that also stocks many vegan items. Some produce is organic. Vegan items include: many brands of veg cheese (Daiya, Follow Your Heart, etc.), non-dairy milks, soy yogurts, Tofurky and other vegan meats, soy ice cream, tofu, Tofutti sour cream and cream cheese, Vegenaise, Earth Balance margarine, plus natural bath & beauty products. There is also a small dry goods health food aisle (gluten-free pastas, organic pasta sauce, organic teas, etc.) and a bulk aisle that stocks TVP in addition to dried beans, grains, and nuts.
